Several officers were able to assist in the selling of raffle tickets for the Farmall 706 tractor restoration project. It was a FANTASTIC way to kick off ticket sales and we greatly appreciate their support as well as those who purchased tickets.

If youd like to buy a chance be sure to see an FFA Officer or member or stop by the booth at the Windsor Harvest Picnic, Half Century of Progress in Rantoul or the Farm Progress Show (possibly at the Shelby County 4-H & Jr Fair as well).
